    <h1>Industries Reference</h1>

    <h2>Cotton Mill</h2>
    <p>Flips when sold via Sell Cotton action. Main source of income. 3 tiles per level.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Coal</th><th>Iron</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Tiles</th><th>Era</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£12</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>+5</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>Canal only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£14</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>+4</td><td>5</td><td>3</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>3</td><td>£16</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>+3</td><td>9</td><td>3</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>4</td><td>£18</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>+2</td><td>12</td><td>3</td><td></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Coal Mine</h2>
    <p>Flips when all coal cubes are removed. Coal must be transported via links.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Iron</th><th>Cubes</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Tiles</th><th>Era</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£5</td><td>0</td><td>2</td><td>+4</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>Canal only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£7</td><td>0</td><td>3</td><td>+7</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>3</td><td>£8</td><td>1</td><td>4</td><td>+6</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>4</td><td>£10</td><td>1</td><td>5</td><td>+5</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Iron Works</h2>
    <p>Flips when all iron cubes are removed. Iron can be used from anywhere (no transport). 1 tile per level.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Coal</th><th>Cubes</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Tiles</th><th>Era</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£5</td><td>1</td><td>4</td><td>+3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>Canal only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£7</td><td>1</td><td>4</td><td>+3</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>3</td><td>£9</td><td>1</td><td>5</td><td>+2</td><td>7</td><td>1</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>4</td><td>£12</td><td>1</td><td>6</td><td>+1</td><td>9</td><td>1</td><td></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Port</h2>
    <p>Flips when used to sell cotton. Also enables access to external/distant markets. 1 tile per level.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Era</th></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£6</td><td>+3</td><td>2</td><td>Canal only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£7</td><td>+3</td><td>4</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>3</td><td>£8</td><td>+4</td><td>6</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>4</td><td>£9</td><td>+4</td><td>9</td><td></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Shipyard</h2>
    <p>Flips immediately when built. High VP but requires developing through lower levels and specific locations. 2 tiles per level.</p>
    <table class="wiki-table">
      <tr><th>Level</th><th>Cost</th><th>Coal</th><th>Iron</th><th>Income</th><th>VP</th><th>Tiles</th><th>Era</th></tr>
      <tr><td>0</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>2</td><td>Must develop through</td></tr>
      <tr><td>1</td><td>£16</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>+2</td><td>10</td><td>2</td><td>Canal only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>2</td><td>£25</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>+1</td><td>18</td><td>2</td><td>Rail only</td></tr>
    </table>

